Fig. 1. Collection localities of 

Lophoura cornuta

in the western North Pacific off the south coast of Hokkaido, northern Japan, in the previous (open circle) and present (closed circles) studies. Localities 1, 2, and 3 are: off Cape Ochiishi (type locality; 
Wilson 1919
), off Cape Shirepa (this paper), and off Shin-Hidaka (this paper), respectively.

